com.mappedin.sdk

Class Map

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mappedin.sdk.Map

  • public class Map
extends java.lang.Object

    A Map belonging to a given venue. Typically represents a certain floor. Give this to a MapView to display to the user.

    The elevation property can be used to determine the order of the floors (first, second, etc).
